{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Martin Bok≈°a Blog","author":"Martin Bok≈°a","gitUrl":"https://github.com/martinboksa/portfolio/","siteUrl":"http://martinboksa.eu"}},"markdownRemark":{"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/bokos/Projects/portfolio/content/blog/necessary-react-libraries/index.sk.md","html":"<p>Za posledn√Ω rok som sa stretol s mno≈æstvom kni≈æn√≠c, ktor√© sa t√Ωkaj√∫ Reactu.\nJe to dan√© najm√§ t√Ωm, ≈æe som nemal veƒæk√© predch√°dzaj√∫ce sk√∫senosti s n√≠m\na z√°rove≈à javascript je tak r√Ωchly jazyk, ≈æe v ≈àom vych√°dza ka≈æd√Ω de≈à\nnov√© mno≈æstvo kni≈æn√≠c.\nR√°d by som si tu odlo≈æil doteraj≈°ie sk√∫senosti a pribl√≠≈æil v√°m, ƒço v≈°etko pova≈æujem\ndnes za nevyhnutn√© vedie≈• pri pr√°ci s Reactom. Kni≈ænice m√¥≈æu pom√¥c≈• hlavne t√Ωm, ktor√≠\ns n√≠m zaƒç√≠naj√∫. Zaƒçiatok som absolvoval s ofici√°lnym <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/tutorial/tutorial.html\">tutori√°lom</a>. Keƒè\nsi ƒçlovek uchop√≠ z√°kladn√© pojmy a zist√≠, ako pribli≈æne <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/faq-structure.html\">≈°trukt√∫rova≈• React projekt</a>, potrebuje dosta≈• nejak√Ω background k aktu√°lnym popul√°rnym kni≈æniciam.\nTu je zoznam kni≈æn√≠c, ktor√© pova≈æujem za d√¥le≈æit√©.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Don‚Äôt overthink it.\nIf you‚Äôre just starting a project, don‚Äôt spend more than five minutes on choosing a file structure.</p>\n<p><cite>React</cite></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"boilerplate\"><a href=\"#boilerplate\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Boilerplate</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app\">create-react-app</a> -\nak nem√°te sk√∫senosti s Reactom, t√°to kni≈ænica v√°m vytvor√≠ boilerplate (kostra projektu) pre va≈°u\naplik√°ciu. Obsahuje v≈°etky nevyhnutn√© konfigur√°cie a z√°vislosti, aby ste mohli\nrovno p√≠sa≈• React a nemuseli sa o niƒç stara≈•. Na zaƒçiatku veƒæa s√∫vislost√≠ e≈°te nemus√≠te vedie≈•. Tento tool sa o to postar√°.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"no-text\"><pre class=\"language-no-text\"><code class=\"language-no-text\">What&#39;s included? React, JSX, ES6, TypeScript and Flow syntax support.</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"state-container\"><a href=\"#state-container\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>State Container</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/react-redux\">Redux</a> - ide o <em>glob√°lny obchod s premenn√Ωmi</em>. Je vhodn√Ω k tomu,\naby ste nemuseli preposiela≈• premenn√∫ cez ƒèal≈°√≠ch <em>x</em> komponent do hƒ∫bky. Tak ju\nnapoj√≠te na glob√°lny obchod. Pou≈æitie napr√≠klad: user data, aktu√°lna t√©ma, stav aplik√°cie, ‚Ä¶\nPou≈æ√≠va sa ƒçasto. Odpor√∫ƒçam si doin≈°talova≈• na vyv√≠janie <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/redux-devtools/lmhkpmbekcpmknklioeibfkpmmfibljd?hl=en\">plugin</a> do chrome.\nAk sa chcete vyhn√∫≈• boilerplate (bez akci√≠, switchov, ‚Ä¶), ktor√Ω je spojen√Ω s Reduxom, odpor√∫ƒçam <a href=\"https://github.com/rematch/rematch\">rematch</a>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.24091778202677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Redux\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/1a291/redux.png 148w,\n/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/2bc4a/redux.png 295w,\n/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png 590w,\n/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/526de/redux.png 885w,\n/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fa2eb/redux.png 1180w,\n/portfolio/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png 1569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/context.html\">React Context</a> - je to pomerne nov√° feature od Reactu.\nJe teoretick√Ωm nahraditeƒæom Reduxu. Tu sa ale vytvor√≠ <code class=\"language-text\">provider</code> d√°t a\njeho vn√∫torn√© komponenty vo vn√∫tri ich vedia ƒç√≠ta≈• pomocou <code class=\"language-text\">consumera</code>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 321px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.40498442367601%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"React Context\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/09b75/react-context.png 148w,\n/portfolio/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/438fb/react-context.png 295w,\n/portfolio/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png 321w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mobxjs/mobx\">MobX</a> - ƒèal≈°ia mo≈ænos≈• stavov√©ho kontajneru.</p>\n<h2 id=\"√∫lo≈æisko\"><a href=\"#%C3%BAlo%C5%BEisko\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>√ölo≈æisko</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marcuswestin/store.js/\">store.js</a> - pom√°ha pri aplik√°ci√°ch zalo≈æen√Ωch na local storage. Star≈°ie iPhone telef√≥ny ho nepodporuj√∫ üòÖ.</p>\n<h2 id=\"serverov√°-komunik√°cia\"><a href=\"#serverov%C3%A1-komunik%C3%A1cia\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serverov√° komunik√°cia</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\">fetch</a> - nat√≠vny pr√≠kaz z ES6,\nktor√Ωm je mo≈æn√© dopytova≈• server. Ch√Ωbaj√∫ mu zatiaƒæ nejak√© funkcie ako napr√≠klad <strong>abort</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/axios/axios\">Axios</a> - roz≈°√≠ren√° verzia <strong>fetch</strong>, zalo≈æen√°\nna XMLHttpRequests.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> axios <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'axios'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\naxios\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/user?ID=12345'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/ky\">Ky</a> - kolega poradil pr√°cu s touto kni≈ænicou, ktor√Ω je zalo≈æen√Ω na fetch. Porovnanie autora Axios vs Ky.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Yes. Axios is based on XMLHttpRequests, while Ky is based on Fetch. Axios has manually implemented a lot of things we get for free with Fetch. Fetch-based libs should be more stable and less buggy in general. Ky also has retry functionality.</p>\n<p><cite><a href=\"https://twitter.com/sindresorhus/status/1037763588826398720\">Sindre Sorhus</a></cite></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client\">Apollo Client</a> - kni≈ænica s plnou podporou\npre <a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>. Pon√∫ka tie≈æ <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/apollo-client-developer-t/jdkknkkbebbapilgoeccciglkfbmbnfm\">dev tools</a> pre Chrome.\nOdpor√∫ƒçam si to pozrie≈•. <strong>GraphQL</strong> v skratke: Viacero dopytov je mo≈æn√© zl√∫ƒçi≈• do jedn√©ho,\nalebo namiesto re≈•azov√Ωch volan√≠ na server ich je mo≈æn√© nahradi≈• za jeden.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/c0967/graphql.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.59539918809201%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"GraphQL\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fb8a0/graphql.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/1a291/graphql.png 148w,\n/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/2bc4a/graphql.png 295w,\n/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fb8a0/graphql.png 590w,\n/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/526de/graphql.png 885w,\n/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/fa2eb/graphql.png 1180w,\n/portfolio/static/f96e4e3efe8134cd40bd5b493015061a/c0967/graphql.png 1478w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2 id=\"css\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2